  "text": "Materials. All chemicals and enzymes were obtained from suppliers described previously [CITATION_1] . T7 sequencing kit was supplied by Pharmacia. DH5aF competent cells were supplied by Gibco/BRL. M 13/pUC # 1212-sequencing and # 1233-reverse-sequencing primers were obtained from New England Biolabs.",
